the organized group of people

00:56:27.306 --> 00:56:28.680
saying, like, this
is now-- we're

00:56:28.680 --> 00:56:29.850
going to agree on the truth.

00:56:29.850 --> 00:56:31.652
And this is going to go forward.

00:56:31.652 --> 00:56:33.860
MATT RIDLEY: Yeah, but I
would argue that even that--

00:56:33.860 --> 00:56:35.460
and correct me if
