sort of putting out

00:56:39.890 --> 00:56:42.539
their standard and
either being rejected

00:56:42.539 --> 00:56:44.080
by the community at
large or accepted

00:56:44.080 --> 00:56:46.550
by the community at large--
much more than-- I mean,

00:56:46.550 --> 00:56:47.890
ICANN, is it called?

00:56:47.890 --> 00:56:50.750
The Internet Committee for the--

00:56:50.750 --> 00:56:52.350
AUDIENCE: Assigned
Names and Numbers.

00:56:52.350 --> 00:56:54.740
MATT RIDLEY: Assigned Names
and Numbers, thank you.

